This app has been made as an assignment to get to know titanium.


INFO
====
Android users will be able to search and read articles on wikipedia.

Iphone users will be able to search and read articles on wikipedia,
       and post the link of the article on twitter. 
       they will also be able to read the tweets of the maker.


BUGS
====
There are still some problems the first time you login on twitter. (the app will freeze)
If you close the app, and launch it again, it will work correctly.


